Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.90,0:03:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as black rukh are available, black djinn are able to regenerate endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無限に　よみがえる。　そして→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And black rukh is spawned by people's resentment and bitterness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:45.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その黒いルフを生み出すものは→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:49.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の恨み。　世を恨み→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,towards the world and towards their fates.
