Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alibaba, I'll hold him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アリババ君　俺が抑える。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつに　とどめを刺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:37.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…。\N（シンドバッド）こいつには→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing wants to kill off everyone \Ninvolved with the monarchy here in Balbadd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この国の王族\N王政に関わった人間を→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:44.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆殺しにする革命の意志がある。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It wants a revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:47.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけは　させてはならない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血でなされた革命は→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A revolution built on bloodshed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:53.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大義さえ掲げれば\Nあらゆる暴力を　正当化する！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,will be used to justify violence by \Nanyone with the smallest moral cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドスッ！\N（シンドバッド）うっ！→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can save us from that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから　国を救い出せるのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring about a bloodless revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:01.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無血革命を掲げた\N君しかいないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シンドバッド）アリババ　斬れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, Alibaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.89,0:06:10.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…　くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわぁ～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおぉ～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:20.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:23.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ…　ぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:26.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪刺さってねぇ。　黒い粒が→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't cut him! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The black bits are repelling my sword! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,剣を避けているだけだ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ！　ああ～…。\Nグオォー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:37.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪アモンよ　俺に力を≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amon, please give me power! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:40.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪今じゃないと遅いんだ！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't stop him now, it'll be too late! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪貫く力を　今…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need the power {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to pierce through him {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:48.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に！　ぐおぉ～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}now! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:51.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっけぇ～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カシム）アリ…　ババ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ali... baba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪カシム？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kassim? {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ！　ぐはっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kassim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カシム…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:16.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んんっ！　くっ…。　ぐはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…。\N≫ドサッ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:27.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（シンドバッド）ううっ…。\N大丈夫ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,モルジアナ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgiana!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.67,0:07:35.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のは？\N魔力操作だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Magoi manipulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,His flow of magoi has been temporarily stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:39.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつの魔力の流れも\N一時的にだが遮断した。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is probably the only time he can't use gravity magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:43.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だけは\N重力魔法を使えないはずだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべての力を　一撃に込めろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Put all of your strength into a decisive blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今なら　必ず貫ける。\Nはい！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to cut him down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:55.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.41,0:08:11.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:15.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪（サブマド）国軍総員　突撃態勢！→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All military forces! Prepare for attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪化け物に　一歩も進ませるな！\Nあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let that monster take another step!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,13th platoon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（バルカーク）第１３小隊　突撃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第２４小隊　左辺へ展開！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,24th platoon, flank left!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（国軍兵士）こんな化け物に→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we'd let a monster take Balbadd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡してたまるかぁ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We must protect our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:42.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この国は　俺たちで\N守らなきゃならないんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:48.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:53.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が頑張らないで　どうするんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:55.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぅ～…　はぁ～。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:09:00.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:02.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手伝う。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:05.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:07.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪みんな！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, everyone! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:23.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:25.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪この一撃で　全部…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll put an end to all of this {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪終わらせるんだ！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in one fell swoop! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:36.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっけぇ～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジュダル）ふっ！\Nあっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:41.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドーン！\N（一同）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:47.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジュダル）よう　これでいいんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you during your recovery, Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:54.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（イスナーン）病み上がりのところ\N悪いな　マギよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あいつは…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's...  {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:10:01.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジュダル）あんなヤツ\Nわざわざ　殺る意味あんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:10:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really worth the effort to kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（イスナーン）\N彼は　何度か　我々の作る流れを→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already destroyed the flow I've tried to build a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妨害している。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今後も　やっかいな存在になる。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's turning out to be an annoyance this time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:12.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のうちに消しておくべきだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We should dispose of him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but first, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それより　一体　何なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:18.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妙に　力が　あふれてきやがるぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I'm brimming with power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:21.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（イスナーン）お前は　堕転した身。→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You are one who has fallen into depravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:24.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒いルフに満ちた今の状態は→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In a situation like this, with so much black rukh around,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力が増すのよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,your power can only grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪最悪だ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The djinn equip that I used all of my concentration on was dispelled. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:32.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あんなに集中させた魔装が\N全部　解けちまった≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪もう　ろくに魔力も残ってない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I barely have any magoi left. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪どうやって\Nあんなヤツらを相手に…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How am I supposed to fight all of them? {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do? {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪どうする？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪どうする!?≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do?! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:45.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ね！\Nきゃあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:53.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マスルール）いいんですか？\N王宮へ行かなくて。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we go to the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well we can't just leave the people like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジャーファル）しかし　こんな惨状を→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:59.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放っておくわけには…。　シン。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is complete pandemonium.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（Ｓナンド）まるで　地獄だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How far are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（Ｌナンド）\Nにいちゃん　どこまで行くのさ～？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:11.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（Ｓナンド）なんとかして\Nこいつを　あの人に返すんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we can give these things back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（Ｍナンド）\Nでも　兄上　このありさまじゃ→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But how are we supposed to find him in this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:16.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人が　どこにいるかなんて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（Ｓナンド）ちくしょう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse it, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:27.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くそっ！　一体どうすれば…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:30.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぅ…。\Nなんで　こんなことに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Someone please make it all stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:33.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か…。　どうか　誰か！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:37.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この国を助けてください…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:43.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（Ｍナンド）兄上。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that in the sky? A bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:48.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な～に？　近づいてくるの…　鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（マスルール）ん？\N（ジャーファル）あれは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:12:08.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（イスナーン）ジュダルよ→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Judal, that djinn is full of dark power, just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは　お前と同じく\N黒い力を宿すジンだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your power to control him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力で支配せよ。　さすれば→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can, he will become your servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:24.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のしもべとなろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and become mine already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:28.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさと　俺のものになりやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:36.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ジュダル）ふ～ん　なるほどな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こいつは　いいや。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is terrible. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:44.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪最悪だ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to do something. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:47.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪何か　手を打たねば≫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「降り注ぐ氷槍」！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.45,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarg Arsarros!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:51.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！　うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぅ…　くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Be good, Sinbad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おとなしくしてな　シンドバッド。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:02.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心しろよ　お前は殺さねぇ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you mine later too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:05.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとで\Nお前も　俺のもんにしてやるよ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ！　やっと　お前を殺す番だぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it's finally time to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.88,0:13:12.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:28.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,グオォーー！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はははっ！　俺のジンは強いぜぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My djinn is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't be able to keep dodging him! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪こんなもの\Nよけ続けられないわ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All we can do right now is run! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪一旦　逃げるしか…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:53.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,モルジアナ…　俺を→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgiana!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you could throw me up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこまで飛ばしてくれないか？\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gathered up all of my remaining power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきためた\N最後の力が残ってるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use it to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで　あいつらに　とどめを刺す。\Nで…　でも→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more enemies now and the \Nblack djinn has been completely healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵も増えたし　魔人の傷も→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:11.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すっかり回復してしまいました。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I just need to whip up something stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　さっきまでよりも→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:17.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと強い力を出すまでだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do as Sinbad said, and use all of the magoi inside of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前に\Nシンドバッドさんが言ってた→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体中の\N魔力を使って…　って手を使えば→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:26.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるはずだ。\Nでも…→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... but... if you do that, you might die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　そんなことをしたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:31.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アリババさんが\N死んでしまうかも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But at this rate, everything we've \Nworked to protect will be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:35.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このままじゃ\N今まで　全員で守ってきたもんが→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部　無駄になるだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やらなきゃいけねぇんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Morgiana!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.45,0:14:41.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,モルジアナ　頼む！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Amon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アモン！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:48.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. {uwahhh ;_________;}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:56.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,へへっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:09.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:14.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と魔人\N二人分の魔力を込めた　この刀→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This sword is loaded with magoi from both me and my djinn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:16.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,受け止められるかなぁ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be able to withstand it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:22.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:25.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,んんっ！\Nおらぁ～！　潰れちまえ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just die already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アモン！\Nピキッ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\Nバキン！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.00,0:15:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:37.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アリババさん！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alibaba!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:40.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,剣が…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Morgiana, throw me up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,モルジアナ　もう一度だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってるんですか！\Nもう剣が…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.55,0:15:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sword is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ残ってる…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も　まだ生きてる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度　やらなきゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, Morgiana! {omg alibabaaaa <3}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:03.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alibaba? {none of these lines are marked as thoughts in the script}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（アラジン）ねえ　アリババくん→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you try so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　君は　そこまでするんだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You always try to take on responsibilities that aren't even yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:18.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君は　いつも\N背負わなくていい責任を→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:21.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人で背負おうとする。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときも→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You did that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときも…→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}and that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのときも　そうだったね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}and that time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕には分かっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that because you're Alibaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:39.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは　君が　アリババくんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はははっ。　はあ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ　僕は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:50.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドォーン！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:55.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:59.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は　力になりたくて→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a source of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君に　手を伸ばすんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always reach my hand out to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度でも。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I always will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Alibaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:14.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　アリババくん。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aladdin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アラジン…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, kiddo. {shoot i can't remember what we used for "chibi"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:20.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと来たか　チビ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:23.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は\Nあのときみたいに　負けないぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause now I've got a djinn too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:27.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も　俺のジンを\N手に入れたんだからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Call out your djinn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:31.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ　お前も　ジンを出しやがれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Ugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウーゴくんかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウーゴくんはね…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ugo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　いないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（モルジアナ　アリババ）あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ウーゴ・回想）((さよなら　アラジン))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Aladdin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:57.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((もう　俺がいなくても大丈夫だ))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine even if I'm not with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't bring out a djinn, then you're \Nnothing but a dumb kid who needs to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジンが出せねぇなら　お前は→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただのガキだな。　死ねよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:10.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The rukh's protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:15.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ？　ルフの加護…→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　違う。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ウーゴくんは　僕に→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.91,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Ugo has left me power! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力を残してくれた≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）おおっ…。\N白い巨人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a white giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's djinn transmutation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:41.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（イスナーン）あれは　ジンの練成術。→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he have possibly obtained-?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:45.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　彼は　手に入れたのか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That has the shape of a djinn, but it's just regular heat magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:49.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ…　巨人の形はしてるけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:52.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単なる　熱魔法じゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've learned how to use magic, Aladdin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:55.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アラジン\N魔法を使えるようになったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:59.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまんねぇガキだなぁ！\Nとっとと　くたばれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:06.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪もう大丈夫だよ　ウーゴくん≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm okay, Ugo. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because you taught me well! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪君が教えてくれたから→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I'm alone, I can do it! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:15.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一人でも　僕は　できる！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「灼熱の双掌」！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Halharl Infigar! {his voice is so pretty :3}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:22.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおっ…。　うわぁ～～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:29.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:33.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おじさん　大丈夫かい？\Nあっ…　ああ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, mister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Morg, could you take Mister Sinbad back into the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　モルさん　おじさんを\N街まで　連れていってくれるかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこに　おじさんが\N会わなきゃいけない人たちが→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some people in there that he needs to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いるんだ。\Nで…　でも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:47.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だから。　さあ　早く。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A letdown of expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（イスナーン）期待が外れたな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That really was just regular heat magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:52.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただの熱魔法だったとは。→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In this country consumed by black rukh, a Magi of that level is no match for Judal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その程度のマギならば→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:58.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今　黒いルフに満ちた　この国で→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ジュダルの敵ではない。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もったいつけて　この程度かよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? That's all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:09.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,がっかりさせんなよ　チビよぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You got my hopes up for nothing, you dumb kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:12.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あいつ　全然効いてねぇ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That didn't work on him at all. {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.97,0:20:15.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪でも　今日のアラジンなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this newly-returned Aladdin seems like he'll be able to handle everything! {thoughts}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:17.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだか　大丈夫な気がする≫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:24.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん…　僕じゃあ　勝てないな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I guess I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:26.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My magic is still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:29.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の魔法は　未完成でね→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can go toe to toe with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のあの人には\N到底　勝てないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君の力が必要だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I need your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君なら\Nあの人と　あの黒いジンに勝てる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0}{emphasize} can defeat him and that black djinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けど…→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:46.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,剣も魔力もねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a sword and I'm out of magoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう　俺は　ろくに戦えねぇんだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことないさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look carefully, Alibaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:20:58.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく見ておくれよ　アリババくん。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:08.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill the royalty! Kill the nobles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王族　貴族を皆殺しにしろ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴン！\Nバカ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! What will that do for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:15.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことして　なんになるんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Things were finally going to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:19.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく　すべてが\N生まれ変わるところだったのよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we decide we would fix our country with our own hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.12,0:21:21.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（国民）自分の国を　自分たちで…→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この手で\Nやり直すって決めたじゃないか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we swear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのとき　そう誓ったはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alibaba, this country still holds the fire of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:30.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アリババくん　この国には→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:33.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望の力が残っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous fire that will allow the people to get on with their lives and overcome their fates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前に進み\N運命を　乗り越えようとする→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:38.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しい力さ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,君が　火をつけたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who sparked that, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who raised their spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:45.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんなの希望の心に。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぅ…　みんな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,諦めてたまるか！\Nああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:55.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前へと生きる命を→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The rukh are drawn by that desire to live! To forge onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:57.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルフ鳥は導く。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.44,0:22:00.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　僕らは　まだ戦える！
